# --- Licensed / third-party research sources — NEVER commit ---
# Primary guard: the source folder by name.
DO NOT CHECK THIS IN/

# Defense-in-depth: even if that folder is renamed or a file is copied
# elsewhere in the tree, these patterns keep the protected content out of git.
*.pdf                      # purchased / licensed journal PDFs (Elsevier et al.)
1-s2.0-*-main.pdf          # Elsevier ScienceDirect article naming
receipt*.png               # purchase receipts (payment info)
receipt*.jpg
*receipt*.pdf

